Yeah.

01:23:33.560 --> 01:23:47.560
Well, it was Auntie Clara's sister, I know what it was, and Auntie Clara lost her sight, so I used to take her and the rest of them, they had no children, wherever they wanted to go, I'd take them, it didn't embarrass me.

01:23:47.560 --> 01:23:59.560
I mean, he used to like a drop of drink, Uncle Perth's did, and there was a club on Conwy Road in Newport, it was men only, right? Pioneer Club.

01:23:59.560 --> 01:24:10.560
And he got that he couldn't go, because I used to take him on a Wednesday, pick him up on the way back home from market, he had a couple hours there with his mates, you know.

01:24:10.560 --> 01:24:13.560
But he got then he couldn't go.

01:24:13.560 --> 01:24:25.560
How am I going to manage, because you know women are allowed in, I was allowed to go in and pick him up, but you couldn't have a drink or anything, you know, but I never drank him alive.

01:24:25.560 --> 01:24:33.560
So I'd go and pick him up on a Wednesday, Kathy said I don't think I'll be able to come much more, he said I'm getting feeble.

01:24:33.560 --> 01:24:47.560
Well, alright then, I wonder could you pick it up for me, I said, but they might not serve me, you know, we'd better make sure they'll, I'll take your crate up and bring it back.

01:24:48.560 --> 01:25:04.560
So the following week he, I went in and Stuart, Stuart, aren't they in the club, he said, you're Kathy, aren't you? Yes, I said, he said, yeah, my wife says she knows you, because she's usually here on a Wednesday.

01:25:04.560 --> 01:25:11.560
Oh, what trouble am I in now? Because I was allowed to go in and pick him up, look he'd be sat in a chair and all that.

01:25:11.560 --> 01:25:22.560
No trouble at all, he said, but we're going to let you come in and pick his case up every week, you bring the empties and you can pay for it for him.

01:25:22.560 --> 01:25:29.560
And then he said you can bring him up to the Christmas party, they'll allow you to stay with him if he wants.

01:25:29.560 --> 01:25:38.560
Oh, I laughed, but you won't be allowed to drink in your mind, but you can stay with him, because his sight was going about you.

01:25:38.560 --> 01:25:39.560
That is so funny, isn't it?

01:25:39.560 --> 01:25:53.560
And it was funny, and my mother was alive then and she said, the jobs you do, you're going to get into trouble one day, I said, you've got to help somebody when they're going blind.

01:25:53.560 --> 01:26:01.560
But then his wife went into hospital, now this was the funniest part, because we've got another farm up the road and they lived on the end, right?

01:26:01.560 --> 01:26:13.560
