01:26:13.560 --> 01:26:28.560
Well then, Auntie Clara was there a fortnight, and I thought, oh my God, he wouldn't allow it, I could go in the kitchen, I tidied that up, but I thought, oh I wonder what the bed is like, you know?

01:26:28.560 --> 01:26:35.560
Because there was news now, she was coming home, I thought, oh my God, he'd been sleeping up there.

01:26:36.560 --> 01:26:49.560
So I said to him, I said, Uncle Perth, I'm coming up tomorrow, alright, he said, do you know, I went up there the following day, I said, I'm going upstairs to strip your bed, I know it all is clean.

01:26:49.560 --> 01:26:54.560
He said, oh you can't go upstairs, he said, people will talk about us.

01:26:54.560 --> 01:27:01.560
Now he was so deep-lied, I said, don't be so stupid.

01:27:01.560 --> 01:27:10.560
He said, well he said, if you do, draw the curtains, so as nobody can see you upstairs.

01:27:10.560 --> 01:27:12.560
Oh my God.

01:27:12.560 --> 01:27:26.560
Well I thought it was hilarious, so that night then, I went in, took him in to see Auntie Clara, she said, hope to be home on the weekend, I said, well I've been up and stripped all the beds and all that, I said, but you'll never guess.

01:27:26.560 --> 01:27:29.560
Oh, what have you done?

01:27:29.560 --> 01:27:34.560
Well I said, he wouldn't let me go upstairs to start with, he said, because people would be talking.

01:27:34.560 --> 01:27:43.560
But I said, he did then, allow me upstairs, but I had to draw the curtains so as nobody could see you, for they were going on the road, I was upstairs changing the bed.

01:27:43.560 --> 01:27:46.560
Oh, just priceless, that's wonderful.

01:27:46.560 --> 01:27:57.560
And we laughed over it, and always, you know, I mean, she finished up in her home, but every so often she'd say, I can never forget Perth being like that with you.

01:27:57.560 --> 01:28:05.560
Well, of course, I was only about 30 and he was about 70-odd, you know, it was so funny, I never dreamt of it.

01:28:05.560 --> 01:28:13.560
I thought, go up and strip the beds and put them all clean and put the cleaner around, because she didn't have a hoover in those days, look.

01:28:13.560 --> 01:28:19.560
