01:28:38.560 --> 01:28:45.560
Yeah, but I was always there, like downstairs, but, you know, I think...

01:28:45.560 --> 01:28:54.560
I laughed, I couldn't believe it, I couldn't stop laughing, I thought, oh my God, would they think like that?

01:28:54.560 --> 01:28:57.560
Well, you'd be amazed, wouldn't you really, sometimes?

